91
00:05:58.652 --> 00:05:59.949
And it had been,

92
00:05:59.949 --> 00:06:05.799
created by very talented team of
developers that have done an amazing job.

93
00:06:05.799 --> 00:06:09.629
But they've been asked to add more and
more and more to it new pieces of

94
00:06:09.629 --> 00:06:14.204
fat every time a client asked for a piece
of functionality, they just added it in.

95
00:06:14.204 --> 00:06:18.081
And it's not a job to kind of
sort out the user experience.

96
00:06:18.081 --> 00:06:21.760
So eventually they got me involved.

97
00:06:21.760 --> 00:06:29.615
And the route that I use when I'm faced
by that is is really, really simple.

98
00:06:29.615 --> 00:06:33.524
It's not rocket science, is this is
a starting point event or you do reach

99
00:06:33.524 --> 00:06:37.450
a point where you need to kind of rethink
the whole structure of the thing.

100
00:06:37.450 --> 00:06:44.184
But what I was basically doing there
was going through screen by screen and

101
00:06:44.184 --> 00:06:50.276
on each screen I would look at every
single element on that screen.

102
00:06:50.276 --> 00:06:54.466
Every menu item, every icon,
every input field,

103
00:06:54.466 --> 00:06:57.878
absolutely everything on that screen and

104
00:06:57.878 --> 00:07:01.790
I ask myself three questions in order,
right?

105
00:07:01.790 --> 00:07:03.535
Question number one, is can I remove this?

106
00:07:03.535 --> 00:07:08.734
What happens if I just remove it,
delete it as getting rid of it, right?

107
00:07:08.734 --> 00:07:11.590
And sometimes it's amazing
how much you can do that.

108
00:07:11.590 --> 00:07:16.603
So for example, icons, right,
that app was riddled with icons,

109
00:07:16.603 --> 00:07:19.297
every option had an icon next to it.

110
00:07:19.297 --> 00:07:25.568
And then you reach a point where it's
like, how does this icon help, right?

111
00:07:25.568 --> 00:07:27.678
Because it was all English speaking.

112
00:07:27.678 --> 00:07:30.033
It wasn't meant to be multilingual.

113
00:07:30.033 --> 00:07:33.791
So it's like, what's this adding to it?

114
00:07:33.791 --> 00:07:35.401
What would happen if I deleted it?

115
00:07:35.401 --> 00:07:38.048
And the answer was, well, nothing.

116
00:07:38.048 --> 00:07:42.387
At which point you go, well,
let's delete it then, right?

117
00:07:42.387 --> 00:07:45.930
But obviously, there are some
things you can't delete, right?

118
00:07:45.930 --> 00:07:51.080
For example, the main menu that was
going down the left hand side, right?

119
00:07:51.080 --> 00:07:52.873
Loads of different options,

120
00:07:52.873 --> 00:07:57.617
all of which were apparently essential
set aside whether they all were or not.

121
00:07:57.617 --> 00:08:02.694
So as I worked down that menu,
my next question was, well,

122
00:08:02.694 --> 00:08:07.377
can I hide some of these
elements in this menu, right?

123
00:08:07.377 --> 00:08:12.021
Instead of they had like 30, I think
something like 30 elements all down a side

124
00:08:12.021 --> 00:08:16.460
menu and it was like, my eyes are bleeding
looking at this list and I said well,

125
00:08:16.460 --> 00:08:19.115
which ones of these are used the most,
right?

126
00:08:19.115 --> 00:08:23.376
To which the answer was well, people
really are only looking at those four.

127
00:08:23.376 --> 00:08:25.790
All right, well,
why are all the others there then?

128
00:08:25.790 --> 00:08:30.590
So I put all the rest under a kind of dot
dot dot thing or hiding things away, or

129
00:08:30.590 --> 00:08:32.165
should we be doing that?

