00:08:32.165 --> 00:08:37.826
Well, if 80% of people are looking at
those four, then let's make it easy for

131
00:08:37.826 --> 00:08:42.492
those 80% of people before we
worry about the 20% looking for

132
00:08:42.492 --> 00:08:44.760
other obscure things, right?

