135
00:08:51.629 --> 00:08:55.469
that was the quick and
easy way of just hiding some stuff, right?

136
00:08:55.469 --> 00:08:57.204
And then, but
sometimes you can't hide things.

137
00:08:57.204 --> 00:09:02.939
